msgid ""
"# Manage\n"
"\n"
"The Manage tab displays workspaces for organising cases, files, attributes, "
"journals, and references.\n"
"Use the [Manage menu](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases) to choose among "
"them.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Files](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_files)\n"
"\n"
"- This menu lets you add and remove empirical data in your project.\n"
"- You can import plain text and many other document types,\n"
"including PDFs, images, audio, and video.\n"
"- You may also import survey data.\n"
"- Before importing text files, you may want to create pseudonyms to protect "
"the privacy of people or organisations.\n"
"- [Help: Import files](qualcoder://help/3.2.-Files/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Cases](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_cases)\n"
"\n"
"- You can use cases to group files together that are related to a topic, "
"person, organisation, or any other empirical entity in your study. \n"
"- This can be useful for organising your data and for running reports on "
"specific groups of files.\n"
"- [Help: Cases](qualcoder://help/3.3.-Cases/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Journals](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_journals)\n"
"\n"
"- Journals are used to record your thoughts when coding and analysing "
"data. \n"
"- The journal window opens separately from the main window so you can move "
"between them easily.\n"
"- [Help: Journals](qualcoder://help/5.2.-Journals/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Attributes](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_attributes)\n"
"\n"
"- Files, cases, and journals can have attributes (variables) that describe "
"their characteristics. \n"
"- They can be used to filter and organise data, and to run reports based on "
"specific criteria. \n"
"- Use this menu to create and manage such attributes. They can be attached "
"to files, cases, and journals directly in the respective workspaces. \n"
"- [Help: Attributes](qualcoder://help/3.4.-Attributes/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage References](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_references)\n"
"\n"
"- Bibliographic references can be imported from NBIB and RIS files.\n"
"- After that, references can be linked to files in the project.\n"
"- [Help: Import References](qualcoder://help/6.1.-Imports-and-Exports/)\n"
msgstr ""
"# Kudeatu\n"
"\n"
"Kudeatu fitxak kasuak, fitxategiak, atributuak, aldizkariak eta "
"erreferentziak antolatzeko lan-espazioak erakusten ditu.\n"
"Haien artean aukeratzeko, erabili [Kudeatu menua](qualcoder://menu/"
"files_and_cases).\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Fitxategiak kudeatu](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_files)\n"
"\n"
"- Menu honek zure proiektuan datu enpirikoak gehitu eta kentzeko aukera "
"ematen dizu.\n"
"- Testu arrunta eta beste dokumentu-mota asko inporta ditzakezu,\n"
"hala nola PDFak, irudiak, audioa eta bideoa.\n"
"- Inkesta-datuak ere inporta ditzakezu.\n"
"- Testu-fitxategiak inportatu aurretik, agian pseudonimoak sortu nahi izango "
"dituzu pertsonak edo erakundeak babesteko.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Fitxategiak inportatu](qualcoder://help/3.2.-Files/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Kasuak kudeatu](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_cases)\n"
"\n"
"- Kasuak erabil ditzakezu zure ikerketako gai, pertsona, erakunde edo beste "
"edozein entitate enpiriko batekin lotutako fitxategiak taldean biltzeko. \n"
"- Hau erabilgarria izan daiteke zure datuak antolatzeko eta fitxategi-talde "
"zehatz batzuei buruzko txostenak egiteko.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Kasuak](qualcoder://help/3.3.-Cases/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Jurnalak Kudeatu](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_journals)\n"
"\n"
"- Jurnalak datuak kodetzen eta aztertzen dituzunean zure pentsamenduak "
"jasotzeko erabiltzen dira. \n"
"- Jurnal-leihoa leiho nagusitik bereizita irekitzen da, beraz, erraz mugi "
"zaitezke bien artean.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Egunkariak](qualcoder://help/5.2.-Journals/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Ezaugarriak kudeatu](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/"
"manage_attributes)\n"
"\n"
"- Fitxategiek, kasuek eta eguneriek ezaugarriak (aldagaiak) izan ditzakete, "
"beren ezaugarriak deskribatzen dituztenak. \n"
"- Datuak iragazi eta antolatzeko, eta irizpenak irizpide zehatzetan "
"oinarrituta exekutatzeko erabil daitezke. \n"
"- Erabili menu hau halako ezaugarriak sortu eta kudeatzeko. Ezaugarri horiek "
"zuzenean atxiki daitezke fitxategiei, kasuei eta eguneriei dagokien lan-"
"espazioetan. \n"
"- [Laguntza: Ezaugarriak](qualcoder://help/3.4.-Attributes/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Erreferentziak kudeatu](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/"
"manage_references)\n"
"\n"
"- Erreferentzia bibliografikoak NBIB eta RIS fitxategietatik inporta "
"daitezke.\n"
"- Horren ondoren, erreferentziak proiektuko fitxategiekin lotu daitezke.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Erreferentziak inportatu](qualcoder://help/6.1.-Imports-and-"
"Exports/)"

#: src/qualcoder/information.py:503
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# Coding\n"
"\n"
"The Coding tab displays workspaces for coding text, PDFs, images, audio, and "
"video.\n"
"Use the [Coding menu](qualcoder://menu/coding) to select an option to "
"begin. \n"
"Note that you can only open a particular coding workspace if that type of "
"data is actually present in the current project. \n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Text](qualcoder://menu/coding/codes)\n"
"\n"
"- Use this workspace to read textual data closely and assign codes to "
"selected passages.\n"
"- You can organise codes in a tree, add memos and annotations, create "
"bookmarks, and mark especially useful segments as important.\n"
"- [Help: Coding text](qualcoder://help/4.1.-Coding-Text/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Images](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_image)\n"
"\n"
"- In this workspace, you can select regions in photographs, diagrams, "
"screenshots, or other visual material and assign codes to them.\n"
"- Coded areas are displayed as coloured rectangles linked to your code "
"system.\n"
"- [Help: Coding images](qualcoder://help/4.4.-Coding-Images/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Audio and Video](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_audio_video)\n"
"\n"
"- Use this workspace to transcribe and/or code time-based media such as "
"interviews, focus groups, and field recordings.\n"
"- [Help: Coding audio and video](qualcoder://help/4.5.-Coding-Audio-and-"
"Video/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code PDFs](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_pdf)\n"
"\n"
"- This workspace allows you to code text directly in PDF documents when you "
"want to keep the original page layout in view.\n"
"- This is useful for articles, reports, and other source material where page "
"position and formatting matter.\n"
"- [Help: Coding PDFs](qualcoder://help/4.3.-Coding-Text-on-PDFs/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Assisted Coding](qualcoder://menu/coding/ai_assisted_coding)\n"
"\n"
"- This loads a variant of the text coding workspace that uses AI to explore "
"your data and suggest segments for a selected code.\n"
"- [Help: AI assisted coding](qualcoder://help/4.2.-AI-Assisted-Coding/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Organiser](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_organiser)\n"
"\n"
"- Use this workspace to reorganise your code system using a graphical, mind-"
"map style interface.\n"
"- You can move, merge, and rename codes and categories as your analytic "
"structure becomes clearer.\n"
"- [Help: Code Organiser](qualcoder://help/4.6-Code-Organiser/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Colour Scheme](qualcoder://menu/coding/colour_scheme)\n"
"\n"
"- This allows you to change the colour scheme of your codes and "
"categories. \n"
"- Special schemes for colour-blind users are available. \n"
msgstr ""
"# Kodeketa\n"
"\n"
"Kodeketa fitxak testuak, PDFak, irudiak, audioa eta bideoa kodetzeko lan-"
"espazioak erakusten ditu.\n"
"Erabili [Kodeketa menua](qualcoder://menu/coding) hasteko aukera bat "
"hautatzeko. \n"
"Kontuan izan kodetze-lanespazio jakin bat soilik ireki dezakezula, datu mota "
"hori egungo proiektuan benetan badagoenean.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Testua kodetzea](qualcoder://menu/coding/codes)\n"
"\n"
"- Erabili lanespazio hau testu-datuak arretaz irakurtzeko eta hautatutako "
"pasarteei kodeak esleitzeko.\n"
"- Kodigoak zuhaitz batean antola ditzakezu, ohar eta anotazioak gehitu, "
"markagailuak sortu, eta bereziki erabilgarriak diren segmentuak garrantzitsu "
"gisa markatu.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Testua kodetzea](qualcoder://help/4.1.-Coding-Text/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Irudien Kodeketa](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_image)\n"
"\n"
"- Lan-espazio honetan, argazki, diagrama, pantaila-argazki edo bestelako "
"material bisualetako eremuak hautatu eta kodeak esleitu diezazkiekezu.\n"
"- Kodetutako eremuak zure kode-sistemarekin lotutako kolorezko laukizuzen "
"gisa bistaratzen dira.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Irudiak kodetzea](qualcoder://help/4.4.-Coding-Images/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Audioa eta bideoa kodetzea](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_audio_video)\n"
"\n"
"- Erabili lan-espazio hau elkarrizketak, foku-taldeak eta eremu-grabazioak "
"bezalako denboran oinarritutako hedabideak transkribatzeko eta/edo "
"kodetzeko.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Audioa eta bideoa kodetzea](qualcoder://help/4.5.-Coding-Audio-"
"and-Video/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [PDFak kodetzea](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_pdf)\n"
"\n"
"- Lan-espazio honek PDF dokumentuetan testua zuzenean kodetzeko aukera "
"ematen dizu, jatorrizko orrialde-egitura ikusgai mantendu nahi duzunean.\n"
"- Artikulu, txosten eta bestelako iturri-materialetarako erabilgarria da, "
"orrialde-posizioa eta formatua garrantzitsuak direnean.\n"
"- [Laguntza: PDFetan testuak kodetzea](qualcoder://help/4.3.-Coding-Text-on-"
"PDFs/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI lagundutako kodetzea](qualcoder://menu/coding/ai_assisted_coding)\n"
"\n"
"- Honek testu kodetze lan-espazioaren aldaera bat kargatzen du, zure datuak "
"aztertzeko eta hautatutako kode baterako segmentuak iradokitzeko adimen "
"artifiziala (AI) erabiltzen duena.\n"
"- [Laguntza: AI bidezko kodetzea](qualcoder://help/4.2.-AI-Assisted-"
"Coding/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Kode Antolatzailea](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_organiser)\n"
"\n"
"- Erabili lan-espazio hau zure kode-sistema berrantolatzeko, grafiko eta "
"gogo-mapa estiloko interfaze baten bidez.\n"
"- Mugi, batu eta berrizendatu ditzakezu kodeak eta kategoriak, zure egitura "
"analitikoa argiago bihurtzen den heinean.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Kode Antolatzailea](qualcoder://help/4.6-Code-Organiser/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Kolore Eskema](qualcoder://menu/coding/colour_scheme)\n"
"\n"
"- Honek zure kode eta kategorien kolore-eskema aldatzeko aukera ematen "
"dizu. \n"
"- Kolore-itsuentzako eskema bereziak eskuragarri daude."

#: src/qualcoder/information.py:560
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# Reports tab\n"
"\n"
"This tab displays tools from both the [Analysis](qualcoder://menu/analysis) "
"and [Reports](qualcoder://menu/reports) menus.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Analysis](qualcoder://menu/analysis)\n"
"\n"
"Use these tools when you want to explore coded segments and relationships in "
"detail.\n"
"\n"
"[Help: Analysis and Reports menu options](qualcoder://help/5.3.-Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Retrieval and segment-based analysis\n"
"\n"
"These tools help you inspect the actual coded material in your project.\n"
"\n"
"- [Code retrieval](qualcoder://menu/analysis/coding_reports) is a flexible "
"analysis tool. It gathers all segments for selected codes or categories and "
"lets you narrow the results by file, case, attributes, or search text.\n"
"- [Codes by text segments](qualcoder://menu/analysis/text_segments_by_codes) "
"generates a table with text segments and all associated codes.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Code relationships and overlaps\n"
"\n"
"Use these tools to examine how codes relate to one another. They only work "
"with text files.\n"
"\n"
"- [Code relations](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_relations) shows "
"proximity, overlap, inclusion, and exact matches between selected codes.\n"
"- [Code co-occurrence](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_co_occurrence) focuses "
"on where two codes overlap or directly touch.\n"
"- [Code text exact matches](qualcoder://menu/analysis/"
"code_text_exact_matches) lists passages where different codes were applied "
"to exactly the same text.\n"
"- [Graph](qualcoder://menu/analysis/view_graph) provides a visual, mind-map "
"style view of linked project elements like codes, cases, files, etc. [Help: "
"Graph](qualcoder://help/5.4.-Graph/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Reports](qualcoder://menu/reports)\n"
"\n"
"Use these tools when you want summaries, comparisons, counts, charts, or "
"exports for reporting purposes.\n"
"\n"
"[Help: Analysis and Reports menu options](qualcoder://help/5.3.-Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Inter-Coder Comparisons\n"
"\n"
"- [Coding comparison](qualcoder://menu/reports/coding_comparison) and "
"[Coding comparison by file](qualcoder://menu/reports/"
"coding_comparison_by_file) are especially useful for collaborative work and "
"inter-coder checking.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Summaries, frequencies, and charts\n"
"\n"
"These reports summarise patterns across the project rather than showing "
"every coded segment in detail.\n"
"\n"
"- [Code frequencies](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_frequencies) counts how "
"often codes and categories have been used.\n"
"- [Code counts by file/case](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_comparison_table) "
"gives a compact overview of where selected codes appear most often.\n"
"- [File summary](qualcoder://menu/reports/file_summary) and [Code summary]"
"(qualcoder://menu/reports/code_summary) give focused overviews of one file "
"or one code at a time.\n"
"- [Charts](qualcoder://menu/reports/charts) visualises distributions and "
"comparisons with diagrams such as bar charts, treemaps, and heatmaps.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Advanced reporting\n"
"\n"
"- [Database queries](qualcoder://menu/reports/sql_statements) gives direct "
"access to the project database for custom analyses. This is most useful when "
"the standard reports do not answer a specific research question in the exact "
"form you need.\n"
msgstr ""
"# Txostenak fitxa\n"
"\n"
"Fitxa honek [Azterketa](qualcoder://menu/analysis) eta [Txostenak]"
"(qualcoder://menu/reports) menuetako tresnak erakusten ditu.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Azterketa](qualcoder://menu/analysis)\n"
"\n"
"Erabili tresna hauek kodetutako segmentuak eta harremanak xehetasunez "
"aztertu nahi dituzunean.\n"
"\n"
"[Laguntza: Azterketa eta Txostenen menuko aukerak](qualcoder://help/5.3.-"
"Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Berreskuratzea eta segmentuetan oinarritutako azterketa\n"
"\n"
"Tresna hauek zure proiektuan dagoen benetako material kodetua aztertzen "
"laguntzen dizute.\n"
"\n"
"- [Kodeen berreskuratzea](qualcoder://menu/analysis/coding_reports) analisi-"
"tresna malgu bat da. Hautatutako kode edo kategoria guztietarako segmentu "
"guztiak biltzen ditu eta emaitzak fitxategi, kasu, atributu edo bilaketa-"
"testuaren arabera murrizteko aukera ematen dizu.\n"
"- [Testu-segmentuak kodeen arabera](qualcoder://menu/analysis/"
"text_segments_by_codes) taula bat sortzen du testu-segmentuekin eta horiekin "
"lotutako kode guztiekin.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Kodeen arteko harremanak eta gainjartzeak\n"
"\n"
"Erabili tresna hauek kodeek elkarrekin nola erlazionatzen diren aztertzeko. "
"Testu-fitxategiekin bakarrik funtzionatzen dute.\n"
"\n"
"- [Kodeen arteko erlazioak](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_relations) "
"hautatutako kodeen arteko hurbiltasuna, gainjartzea, inklusioa eta zehatz-"
"mehatzko bat-etortzeak erakusten ditu.\n"
"- [Kodeen baterako agerpena](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_co_occurrence) "
"bi kodeek non gainjartzen diren edo elkar ukitzen duten zentratzen da.\n"
"- [Kodeen testu-berdinketak](qualcoder://menu/analysis/"
"code_text_exact_matches) zerrendatzen ditu pasarteak, non kode desberdinak "
"testu berean zehatz-mehatz aplikatu diren.\n"
"- [Grafikoa](qualcoder://menu/analysis/view_graph) proiektu lotutako "
"elementuen (kodeak, kasuak, fitxategiak, etab.) mapa mental estilo bisuala "
"eskaintzen du. [Laguntza: Grafikoa](qualcoder://help/5.4.-Graph/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Txostenak](qualcoder://menu/reports)\n"
"\n"
"Erabili tresna hauek laburpenak, konparazioak, kontaketak, grafikoak edo "
"esportazioak txostenetarako nahi dituzunean.\n"
"\n"
"[Laguntza: Azterketa eta txostenen menuko aukerak](qualcoder://help/5.3.-"
"Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Kodetzaileen arteko konparazioak\n"
"\n"
"- [Kodetze-konparaketa](qualcoder://menu/reports/coding_comparison) eta "
"[Fitxategiaren arabera kodetze-konparaketa](qualcoder://menu/reports/"
"coding_comparison_by_file) bereziki erabilgarriak dira lankidetza-lanerako "
"eta kodetzaileen arteko egiaztapenerako.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Laburpenak, maiztasunak eta grafikoak\n"
"\n"
"Txosten hauek proiektu osoan zehar ereduak laburbiltzen dituzte, segmentu "
"kodifikatu guztiak xehetasunez erakutsi beharrean.\n"
"\n"
"- [Kodeen maiztasunak](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_frequencies) kode eta "
"kategoria kopurua zenbat aldiz erabili den kontatzen du.\n"
"- [Kode kopuruak fitxategi/kasuaren arabera](qualcoder://menu/reports/"
"code_comparison_table) hautatutako kodeek non agertzen diren maiztasun "
"handienarekin laburbilduko ikuspegi bat ematen du.\n"
"- [Fitxategiaren laburpena](qualcoder://menu/reports/file_summary) eta "
"[Kodearen laburpena](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_summary) fitxategi edo "
"kode bakar bati buruzko ikuspegi zehatzak eskaintzen dituzte.\n"
"- [Grafikoak](qualcoder://menu/reports/charts) banaketak eta konparazioak "
"bistaratzen ditu diagramen bidez, hala nola zutabe-grafikoetan, zuhaitz-"
"mapetan eta bero-mapetan.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Txosten aurreratuak\n"
"\n"
"- [Datu-base kontsultak](qualcoder://menu/reports/sql_statements) "
"proiektuaren datu-basera sarbide zuzena ematen du azterketa pertsonalizatuak "
"egiteko. Hau da erabilgarriena txosten estandarrak ez badute erantzuten "
"ikerketa-galdera zehatz bati behar duzun formatu zehatzean."

#: src/qualcoder/information.py:621
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# AI Agent\n"
"\n"
"Here, you can interact with the [AI Agent](qualcoder://help/5.1.-AI-chat-"
"based-analysis/) to\n"
"explore your empirical text data, get suggestions for coding, obtain "
"feedback on your codes or memos,\n"
"and generate summaries and reports. To begin, use the [\"New\" button]"
"(qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new) at \n"
"the bottom left and choose one of the options described below.\n"
"\n"
"{{AI_WARNING_BLOCK}}\n"
"\n"
"## [Chat with the AI Agent](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_general_chat)\n"
"\n"
"- This is the default starting point for an open-ended analysis or any other "
"task.\n"
"- You can also ask for help using QualCoder.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Topic Exploration](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/"
"new_topic_exploration)\n"
"\n"
"- Search and explore a topic or question across the whole corpus of project "
"data.\n"
"- This option opens a dialog where you define the topic and select which "
"data to include in the analysis.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Text Analysis](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_text_analysis)\n"
"\n"
"- Analyse a selected text passage from your empirical material in detail.\n"
"- This will switch to the text coding workspace and let you select a passage "
"for analysis.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Code Analysis](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_code_analysis)\n"
"\n"
"- Discuss your codings with the AI Agent, compare different codes, generate "
"subcodes, or create reports.\n"
"- This will also open a dialog to select the code(s) and data you want to "
"include in the analysis.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## Other Options\n"
"- The [AI permissions](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/permissions) control at the "
"bottom left lets you choose what \n"
"the AI Agent is allowed to do in your project.\n"
"- Open the [AI menu](qualcoder://menu/ai) for more options, for example to "
"edit predefined prompts in the\n"
"[prompt library](qualcoder://menu/ai/ai_prompts), or start [AI assisted "
"coding](qualcoder://menu/ai/ai_search_and_coding).\n"
msgstr ""
"# AI Agent\n"
"\n"
"Hemen, [AI Agent](qualcoder://help/5.1.-AI-chat-based-analysis/)arekin "
"elkarreragin dezakezu zure testu-datuen azterketa empirikoa egiteko, "
"kodifikaziorako iradokizunak jasotzeko, zure kode edo memoen inguruko "
"iritzia jasotzeko, eta laburpenak eta txostenak sortzeko. Hasieratzeko, "
"erabili beheko ezkerrean dagoen [\"New\" botoia](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/"
"new) eta hautatu behean deskribatzen diren aukeretako bat.\n"
"\n"
"{{AI_WARNING_BLOCK}}\n"
"\n"
"## [AI agentearekin txateatu](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/"
"new_general_chat)\n"
"\n"
"- Hau da amaierarik gabeko analisi baterako edo beste edozein zereginetarako "
"lehenetsitako abiapuntua.\n"
"- QualCoder erabiliz laguntza eskatzeko aukera ere duzu.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Gaien Esplorazioa](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/"
"new_topic_exploration)\n"
"\n"
"- Proiektuaren datu-korpus osoan gai edo galdera bat bilatu eta esploratu.\n"
"- Aukera honek elkarrizketa-koadro bat irekiko du, non gaia definituko duzun "
"eta azterketan sartuko diren datuak hautatuko dituzun.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Testu-azterketa](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_text_analysis)\n"
"\n"
"- Zure material enpirikoko hautatutako testu-pasarte bat xehetasunez "
"aztertuko duzu.\n"
"- Honek testu-kodetze lan-eremura aldatuko zaitu eta azterketarako pasarte "
"bat hautatzeko aukera emango dizu.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Kodearen Azterketa](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_code_analysis)\n"
"\n"
